question_text:
For what values of $$m,$$ does the system of equations 
$$$\matrix{
   {3x + my = m}  \cr 
   {2x - 5y = 20}  \cr 

 } $$$
has solution satisfying the conditions $$x > 0,\,y > 0.$$

Find the solution set of the system 
$$$\matrix{
   {x + 2y + z = 1;}  \cr 
   {2x - 3y - w = 2;}  \cr 
   {x \ge 0;\,y \ge 0;\,z \ge 0;\,w \ge 0.}  \cr 

 } $$$
